{"tid":900258,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"史丹李或繼續在《復仇者聯盟聯4》中客串 他還想留驚喜給大家","createTime":"2018-11-13T05:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T03:32:42.000Z","uid":49391,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b9ef554f15ee4dc7ae34240eedba2304166bde39","tid":900258,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;漫威之父&rdquo;史丹李的逝世成為今年又一個令人難過的消息，無數粉絲為之感到傷心。漫威電影宇宙（MCU）從誕生開始，史丹李幾乎客串了每一部電影，那麼在他逝世後，未來上映的漫威宇宙電影中還會有他的身影嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e23Z91D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe23Z91D.jpg&h=c338ddd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今天漫威工作室總裁凱文・費奇在接受Variety採訪時透露，斯坦李老爺子未來還會出現在MCU未來的幾部電影當中客串，不過他並未透露會是哪幾部電影，因為史丹李也想留驚喜給大家。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;史丹李漫威工作室的所有人都非常親切，他非常鼓舞人心。而且他還是一個謙虛的人，他不會突然出現然後教你怎麼做，但他能夠用自己的精神感染大家跟隨他的步伐。&rdquo;凱文・費奇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ron7Oi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ron7Oi.gif&h=4cfeac1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Hbw08j.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Hbw08j.gif&h=427a3bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而據《娛樂週刊》報導，斯坦李將不會在《變種特攻：黑鳳凰》中客串登場，目前可能性最大的是他的客串彩蛋會直到2019年的《驚奇隊長》和《復仇者聯盟4》當中，而在這部電影之後的《蜘蛛俠：英雄遠征》則尚未確定會有斯坦李的彩蛋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3ANztj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3ANztj.jpg&h=3d466d46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b1256ee4b23089a19f8392298063ea88b1df828","tid":900258,"uid":186784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2f981b0ab388dd0da66ecea34b9c0d67384a5e","tid":900258,"uid":222016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}